{"tid":915782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【C朗】最誠實的男人　簡迪交稅多過兩大巨企","createTime":"2018-11-25T08:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T11:58:48.000Z","uid":20634,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7835634e7cea8d94da52a510ef79c8051b1bbb72","tid":915782,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181124/photo/bkn-20181124211000191-1124_00882_001_01p.jpg?20181124211328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181124211000191-1124_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20181124211328&h=0c928826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181124/photo/bkn-20181124211000191-1124_00882_001_02p.jpg?20181124211328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181124211000191-1124_00882_001_02p.jpg%3F20181124211328&h=548c210e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車路士中場尼高路簡迪日前續約至2023年，人工亦由15萬鎊周薪，大增至29萬鎊，成為車仔最高薪球員。英國傳媒幫呢位法國國腳計數，指佢加人工之後，每年需要向英國政府交670萬鎊稅，仲多過兩大美國企業星巴克同亞馬遜上年交畀英國政府嘅稅款總和。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜8月公布2017年業績，佢哋喺英國業務利潤增加300%，本應交460萬鎊稅，但因可延後繳交，實際只係交咗唔夠一半。至於星巴克上年喺英國利潤達1.62億鎊，但只交咗450萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n《足球解密》早前爆料，指車仔曾建議尼高路簡迪開設離岸公司避稅，但佢份人太老實，斷然拒絕，令到自己實際收到嘅人工少咗一大截。不<span style=\"color: red;\">過，起碼心安理得，唔使好似C朗之前咁，因為逃稅被西班牙政府告上法庭。</span>"},{"pid":"b4964f0c483f343b8cadf3685ae6d0eb1d8c1c90","tid":915782,"uid":166126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9d265a80980c74f332fd12d6066c8efb94abf9","tid":915782,"uid":58140,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:32:48.000Z","msg":"毒撚怕煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666b68925899b0ec645612f65f8e7d1db3b29dba","tid":915782,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"